textAnnotations.description:
THE ONLY
ONE WHO
CARED..
"OUTRAGEOUS!
AT THIS RATE, THE
OSCARS WILL RUN
LOS ANGELES TIMES
THREE HOURS,
29 MINUTES
AND 17
SECONDS!"
HEY! WHY
DONT YOU JOIN US?
WE'RE ALL BETTING
ON WHETHER
ENNIFER LAWRENCE
WILL FALL DOWN
AGAIN!
